description:
Glad Compostable Lawn and Leaf Extra Large Trash Bags are built to tackle any yard. They compost completely, quickly and safely in municipal composting facilities just like paper, yard trimmings and food scraps do. These compostable lawn and leaf bags are certified by the industry standards authority, BPI and meet the requirements of municipal compost programs and ASTM D6400. The built in flaps provide easy closure with no need for inconvenient twist ties that can be misplaced. The flaps also help keep the bag securely shut to avoid messy trash disasters as you transport it. These 33 gallon size compostable bags are perfect for tough yard waste and easy on the environment.


Directions: To close bag and keep trash inside, simply cross-tie the four flaps. For best results, use within one year of purchase. Store bags in a cool, dry area. Wet grass clippings may accelerate bag decomposition. These trash bags have been designed for use in municipal composting programs, not for backyard composting.

Warnings: Plastic bags can be dangerous. To avoid danger of suffocation, keep all plastic bags away from babies and children. Do not use plastic bags in cribs, beds, carriages or playpens.
